Emery Air Freight Corp, whichacquired controlling interest in Purolator Courier Corp &lt;PCC>,said it has named John Kilcullen executive vice president andchief operating officer of Purolator.    Previously, Emery said Kilcullen was Purolator's executivevice president of operations.    Emery said Kilcullen now heads the Purolator executivemanagement team and reports to Emery President Denis McCarthy. Reuter&#3;